{"tid":1398213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發召集］想幫香港警察登上健力士紀錄嘅入嚟！","createTime":"2019-08-02T17:20:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T08:45:51.000Z","uid":251001,"like":580,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"5d7bfe8291347f345ec40ae2ff6a3261f8712326","tid":1398213,"uid":251001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:20:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">本組織</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">（名稱待定）</span><br />\n<br />\n為全香港廣大市民<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">紀錄香港警察</span></span><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一切行為同埋各類型嘅數據</span></span><br />\n<br />\n幫助香港警察挑戰<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">世界<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">健</span><span style=\"color: teal;\">力</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">士</span></span>紀錄</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n進一步令香港警察 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[orange]揚威國際[/red]</span> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[orange]光宗耀祖[/red]</span><br />\n<br />\n世界紀錄係國際矚目嘅事項  國際關注嘅情況下<br />\n港共政府嘅一舉一動都隨時登上國際頭版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n健力士紀錄成功必定係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最強文宣</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我們現在誠邀各位有興趣嘅手足<br />\n或*專業人士加入我哋<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">（非遊行人士/公務員/律師/會計師）</span><br />\n協助我哋紀錄唔同嘅數字<br />\n</span><br />\n組織TG Group Link<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於健力士紀錄嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">紀錄規則</span></span>可以睇返呢個post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1398160\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1398160</a><br />\n我哋需要你嘅一分力！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嚟緊嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">旺角史上最短遊行路線</span></span> <br />\n將會係我哋嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">主線任務</span>！<br />\n協助香港警察一同挑戰健力士紀錄！！<br />\n如果行動成功 日後將會加強此方面文宣力度！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"90f2bb198a9b2b2c813fdf43fbe6d2e92c98242f","tid":1398213,"uid":254809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:20:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2452092948fa6877eb3ca7e8672a3213b4aaea54","tid":1398213,"uid":251001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:21:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光</span></span>"},{"pid":"6b624ee3556ce4e409334f6be108ef3d026aa280","tid":1398213,"uid":251001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:21:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">復</span></span>"},{"pid":"7493aac97119da554a779188cafbc791fda0a3f3","tid":1398213,"uid":254809,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:21:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香</span></span>"},{"pid":"1c00dc9f92f9fac3658845d9b6520041a200f1d4","tid":1398213,"uid":251001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:21:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香</span></span>"},{"pid":"31fc5c9f0dccc9779369634f7ecd502054a24dbd","tid":1398213,"uid":251001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:21:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港</span></span>"},{"pid":"f0acc5ce9219694abf981aea5c2dbf0f0f9d1a43","tid":1398213,"uid":251001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"